+			installed.
+		      </entry>
+		    </row>
+
+		    <row>
+		      <entry><computeroutput>v</computeroutput></entry>
+		      <entry>-</entry>
+		      <entry>
+			the package is virtual.
+		      </entry>
+		    </row>
+
