+		      <entry>
+			the package has been unpacked but not
+			configured.
+		      </entry>
+		    </row>
+
+		    <row>
+		      <entry><computeroutput>C</computeroutput></entry>
+		      <entry>-</entry>
+		      <entry>
+			half-configured: the package's configuration
